title: Torchlight.II.Update.5-RELOADED
description:
Torchlight.II.Update.5-RELOADED

  
Note: We usually do updates with everything included, but for this one you
  need our Update 4 installed first. This is a very minor update, and no data
  files have changed.
  
  Updated:
  
  This is a small patch to fix a single crash issue with effects based on
  proximity, usually triggered in multiplayer by zoning with Battle Rage
  enabled.
